HEADWORD: Assailment
<hw>As*sail"ment</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
power of assailing; attack; assault.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His most frequent <qex>assailment</qex> was the headache.</q>
